divs: Sighting DetailsStanding ouside looking at stars and saw object far up in sky moving steady fromnorth to east towards the cascade mts. Sawanother about 5 minustes later heading same way. I thought it was up to high to be plane and no blinking lights on it just dull looking star that was very steady going along. I felt in awh. It just went so far that I couldn't see it any more
Summary: went north to east in 3 minutes saw 2 of them
